    <div class="contact-body">
        <div class="report-details">

            <h2>Our team</h2>
            <img src="team.jpg" alt="team">
            <p>At SDG 6, we believe in the power of community engagement. You can actively contribute to our mission by
                reporting rivers, ponds, lakes, and other water bodies that deserve recognition on our website. Help us
                build a comprehensive database of water resources around the world.</p>

        </div>
        <form action="/add" method="post">
            <h2>Connect with Us: Report a Water Body</h2>
            <div class="input-details">
                <label for="name">Full name</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name">
            </div>
            <div class="input-details">
                <label for="email">Email</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email">
            </div>
            <div class="input-details">
                <label for="contact no">Contact no(optional)</label>
                <input type="tel" id="contact" name="contact">
            </div>
            <h4>Water body details</h4>
            <div class="input-water-details">
                <label for="water-name">Name of Water Body</label>
                <input type="text" name="nameOfWater">
            </div>

            <div class="input-water-details">
                <label for="lat">Lat(optional)</label>
                <input type="text" id="lat" name="LAT">
            </div>
            <div class="input-water-details">
                <label for="lon">Lon(optional)</label>
                <input type="text" id="lon" name="LON">
            </div>
            <div class="input-water-details">
                <label for="address">Address</label>
                <input type="text" id="address" name="ADDRESS">
            </div>
            <div class="input-water-details">
                <label for="State">State</label>
                <input type="text" id="State" name="STATE">
            </div>
            <div class="input-water-details">
                <fieldset border="1">
                    <legend>Type of Water Body:</legend>
                    <label for="river">
                        <input type="radio" id="river" name="typeOfWater" value="river">
                        River
                    </label>
                    <br>
                    <label for="lake">
                        <input type="radio" id="lake" name="typeOfWater" value="lake">
                        Lake
                    </label>
                    <br>
                    <label for="pond">
                        <input type="radio" id="pond" name="typeOfWater" value="pond">
                        Pond
                    </label>
                    <br>
                    <label for="other">
                        <input type="radio" id="Other" name="typeOfWater" value="other">
                        Other
                    </label>
                    <br>
                    <label for="story">Provide a Brief Story About the Water Body:</label>
                    <br>
                    <textarea name="STORY" id="story" cols="80" rows="5"></textarea>
                </fieldset>

            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Submit</button>
    </div>
    



    </form>
    </div>
    <div class="why-report">
        <h2>Why Report?</h2>
        <p>By reporting water bodies, you contribute to a global initiative to highlight the importance of sustainable
            water management. Your input helps us raise awareness about the diversity of water resources worldwide and
            promotes the responsible use and preservation of these vital ecosystems.</p>
        <h2>Get Involved Today!</h2>
        <p>Join us in building a comprehensive and informative platform that celebrates the richness of the world's
            water bodies. Report a water body now and be a part of the movement toward a sustainable water future.

            [Link to Reporting Form]

            Thank you for your active participation in the SDG 6 community!</p>
    </div>


